# ⚡ Utility Usage Prediction Tool
### CodeVedX AI/ML Internship — Project 1

A Python console application that tracks monthly utility usage (electricity, water, gas) and uses **Linear Regression** to predict future consumption.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Menu-driven console interface (9 options)
- ✅ Add, view, update, delete monthly records
- ✅ CSV file storage using Pandas
- ✅ ML model training with scikit-learn (Linear Regression)
- ✅ Predict next month's utility usage
- ✅ Export data to CSV
- ✅ Input validation & exception handling
- ✅ Model persistence (save/load with pickle)

---

