## 🤖 ML Model Details

| Property | Value |
|---|---|
| Algorithm | Linear Regression (scikit-learn) |
| Feature | Month index (1, 2, 3, ... N) |
| Targets | Electricity, Water, Gas, Bill |
| Evaluation | R² Score |
| Storage | Pickle (.pkl) |

